<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<title>Denoms - EZcash API</title>
<%= render partial: 'docs/v1/shared/head' %>
<body>

<!-- !PAGE CONTENT! -->
<div class="w3-content" style="max-width:1500px">
  
<!-- Header -->
<header class="w3-panel w3-center w3-opacity" >
<%= render partial: 'docs/v1/shared/navigation' %>
</header>

<div class="w3-row-padding w3-grayscale" style="margin-bottom:128px">
  <div class="w3-half">
    <h1>Denoms</h1>
    <p>
    Denom objects allow you to perform calls on denoms. 
    The API allows you to create, delete, and update denoms. 
    You can retrieve individual denoms as well as a list of all denoms.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="w3-half" style="padding-right:200px">
    <div style="float:right;">
      <h5>END POINTS</h5>
      POST /api/v1/denoms
      <br>
      GET /api/v1/denoms/:id?dev_id=:device_id
      <br>
      PUT /api/v1/denoms/:id?dev_id=:device_id
      <br>
      DELETE /api/v1/denoms/:id?dev_id=:device_id
      <br>
      GET /api/v1/denoms
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="w3-row-padding w3-grayscale" style="margin-bottom:128px">
  <div class="w3-half">
    <h1>The Denom Object</h1>
    <h5>Attributes</h5>
    <hr>
    <b>cassette_nbr</b> <small>unique identifier - integer (:id)</small>
    <hr>
    <b>cassette_id</b> <small>varchar</small>
    <hr>
    <b>denomination</b> <small>float</small>
    <hr>
    <b>dev_id</b> <small>integer</small>
    <hr>
    <b>currency_type</b> <small>integer</small>
  </div>

  <div class="w3-half" style="padding-right:200px">
    <div style="float:right;">
      <h5>THE DENOM OBJECT</h5>
      <pre>
        {
          "denomination": 50.0,
          "dev_id": 99,
          "cassette_nbr": 2,
          "cassette_id": "2",
          "currency_type": null
        }
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="w3-row-padding w3-grayscale" style="margin-bottom:128px">
  <div class="w3-half">
    <h1>Create a Denom</h1>
    <h5>Parameters</h5>
    <hr>
    <b>cassette_nbr</b> <small>required</small>
    <hr>
    <b>cassette_id</b> <small>required</small>
    <hr>
    <b>denomination</b> <small>required</small>
    <hr>
    <b>dev_id</b> <small>required</small>
    <hr>
    <b>currency_type</b> <small>optional</small>
  </div>

  <div class="w3-half" style="padding-right:200px">
    <div style="float:right;">
      <h5>POST /api/v1/denoms</h5>
      <h5>RESPONSE</h5>
      <pre>
        {
          "denomination": 50.0,
          "dev_id": 99,
          "cassette_nbr": 2,
          "cassette_id": "2",
          "currency_type": null
        }
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="w3-row-padding w3-grayscale" style="margin-bottom:128px">
  <div class="w3-half">
    <h1>Retrieve a Denom</h1>
    <p>Retrieves the details of an existing Denom. You need only supply the Denom cassette_nbr as the unique identifier, along with the dev_id that was returned upon Denom creation.</p>
    <h5>Parameters</h5>
    <hr>
    <b>dev_id</b> <small>required</small>
    <hr>
    <h5>Returns</h5>
    <hr>
    <p>Returns a Denom object if a valid identifier was provided.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="w3-half" style="padding-right:200px">
    <div style="float:right;">
      <h5>GET /api/v1/denoms/:id?dev_id=:device_id</h5>
      <h5>RESPONSE</h5>
      <pre>
        {
          "denomination": 50.0,
          "dev_id": 99,
          "cassette_nbr": 2,
          "cassette_id": "2",
          "currency_type": null
        }
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="w3-row-padding w3-grayscale" style="margin-bottom:128px">
  <div class="w3-half">
    <h1>Update a Denom</h1>
    <p>Updates the specified Denom by setting the values of the parameters passed. Any parameters not provided will be left unchanged.</p>
    <p>This request accepts mostly the same arguments as the Denom creation call.</p>
    <h5>Parameters</h5>
    <hr>
    <b>cassette_nbr</b> <small>required</small>
    <hr>
    <b>cassette_id</b> <small>required</small>
    <hr>
    <b>denomination</b> <small>required</small>
    <hr>
    <b>dev_id</b> <small>required</small>
    <hr>
    <b>currency_type</b> <small>optional</small>
  </div>

  <div class="w3-half" style="padding-right:200px">
    <div style="float:right;">
      <h5>PUT /api/v1/denoms/:id</h5>
      <h5>RESPONSE</h5>
      <pre>
        {
          "denomination": 50.0,
          "dev_id": 99,
          "cassette_nbr": 2,
          "cassette_id": "2",
          "currency_type": null
        }
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="w3-row-padding w3-grayscale" style="margin-bottom:128px">
  <div class="w3-half">
    <h1>Delete a Denom</h1>
    <p>Permanently deletes a Denom. It cannot be undone.</p>
    <h5>Parameters</h5>
    <hr>
    <b>dev_id</b> <small>required</small>
    <hr>
    <h5>Returns</h5>
    <hr>
    <p>Message: "Denom deleted". If the Denom identifier does not exist, this call raises an error.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="w3-half" style="padding-right:200px">
    <div style="float:right;">
      <h5>DELETE /api/v1/denoms/:id?dev_id=:device_id</h5>
      <h5>RESPONSE</h5>
      <pre>
          Denom deleted
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="w3-row-padding w3-grayscale" style="margin-bottom:128px">
  <div class="w3-half">
    <h1>List All Denoms</h1>
    <p>Returns a list of your denoms. The denoms are returned in the order they were created, with the oldest denoms appearing first.</p>
    <h5>Parameters</h5>
    <hr>
    <b>denomination</b> <small>optional</small>
    <hr>
    <b>dev_id</b> <small>optional</small>
    <hr>
    <b>cassette_nbr</b> <small>optional</small>
    <hr>
    <b>cassette_id</b> <small>optional</small>
    <hr>
    <b>currency_type</b> <small>optional</small>
    <hr>
    <h5>Returns</h5>
    <hr>
    <p>
      An array of denoms. Passing optional parameter(s) will result in filtering the denoms by the passed parameter(s). 
      Each entry in the array is a separate denom object. Use limit parameter to specify the number of objects in the array.
      If no more denoms are available, the resulting array will be empty. 
      This request should never raise an error.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="w3-half" style="padding-right:200px">
    <div style="float:right;">
      <h5>GET /api/v1/denoms</h5>
      <h5>RESPONSE</h5>
      <pre>
        [
          {
            "denomination": 50.0,
            "dev_id": 99,
            "cassette_nbr": 2,
            "cassette_id": "2",
            "currency_type": null
          },
          {...},
          {...}
        ]
      </pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<!-- End Page Content -->
</div>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="w3-container w3-padding-64 w3-light-grey w3-center w3-large"> 
  <p>Powered by <a href="https://www.tranact.com" target="_blank" class="w3-hover-text-green">Tranact</a></p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
